as long as scape (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 18–27" captionStartId="F4" captionText="Figures 18 - 27. Eriastichus spp. head and antenna in lateral view, male holotypes 18 E. decoris 19 E. denotatis 20 E. dotaensis 21 E. derilis 22 E. diadrys 23 E. ebulis 24 E. egrestis 25 E. ellipsis 26 E. drupis 27 E. eleagnis." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1019.60364.figures18-27" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/512581" pageId="0" pageNumber="35">22</figureCitation>
